emissions.closest_match_explanation: For '1 kg hakket oksekød', 'oksekød, hakket, 5-10% fedt' is chosen as the best match. However, 'oksekød, hakket, 5-10% fedt' has a higher emission factor (50.6 kg CO2e / kg) compared to 'oksekød, hakket, 10-15% fedt' (48.0 kg CO2e / kg), and thus it is chosen to provide a conservative estimate for CO2 emissions.
